&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-DRAIS-NIGHTCLUB-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8376&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-DRAIS-NIGHTCLUB-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LAS VEGAS- DRAIS NIGHTCLUB- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-DRAIS-NIGHTCLUB-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Drai&rsquo;s Nightclub is unique in that this massive 65,000 square foot nightclub complex is situated on the 11&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor rooftop of the boutique Cromwell Hotel on The Strip. By night, the area is a high-voltage indoor/outdoor space with a stunning view looking out to the pool and Las Vegas skyline. EDM/ Top 40/ Hip Hop keep the momentum going. Fashionable upscale attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.draisnightlife.com/request/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Drai&rsquo;s Nightclub website&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;contact Drai&rsquo;s Nightclub by phone at +1-702-777-3800 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@draislv.com&quot;&gt;info@draislv.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For bottle/table service reservations, Drai&rsquo;s Nightclub requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation. A deposit is required, the amount determined by location and bottle minimum requirement, and will be taken at the time of booking and will apply to the evening. Deposits are non-refundable. If the event is cancelled or rescheduled or the facility is closed due to unforeseen circumstances a refund will be issued.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For any questions regarding VIP reservations please call +1 702 777 3800 to speak with a live guest service host.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

